e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06131430%2Fsupport-for-Palestine.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20letter%20and%20note%20below%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nplusonemag.com%2Fonline-only%2Fonline-only%2Fa-dangerous-conflation%2F%3Faffid%3Dx%5C%22%3Efirst%20published%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nplusonemag.com%2Fonline-only%2Fonline-only%2Fa-dangerous-conflation%2F%3Faffid%3Dx%5C%22%3En%2B1%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nplusonemag.com%2Fonline-only%2Fonline-only%2Fa-dangerous-conflation%2F%3Faffid%3Dx%5C%22%3Emagazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20group%20of%20Jewish%20writers%20drafted%20this%20letter%20after%20seeing%20an%20old%20argument%20gain%20new%20power%3A%20the%20claim%20that%20critiquing%20Israel%20is%20antisemitic.%20Editors%20at%20a%20corporate-owned%20magazine%20were%20prepared%20to%20publish%20the%20letter%2C%20but%20their%20lawyers%20advised%20against%20it.%20The%20writers%20share%20this%20letter%20in%20solidarity%20with%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20speak%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinian%20freedom.%20Add%20your%20name%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeNhU6EmFLHWUr8wBA1K2khoUu2HAOYR5JLJWiq2_e3eWSr0Q%2Fviewform%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20Jewish%20writers%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20activists%20who%20wish%20to%20disavow%20the%20widespread%20narrative%20that%20any%20criticism%20of%20Israel%20is%20inherently%20antisemitic.%20Israel%20and%20its%20defenders%20have%20long%20used%20this%20rhetorical%20tactic%20to%20shield%20Israel%20from%20accountability%2C%20dignify%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20multibillion-dollar%20investment%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20obscure%20the%20deadly%20reality%20of%20occupation%2C%20and%20deny%20Palestinian%20sovereignty.%20Now%2C%20this%20insidious%20gagging%20of%20free%20speech%20is%20being%20used%20to%20justify%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20military%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20and%20to%20silence%20criticism%20from%20the%20international%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20condemn%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20mourn%20such%20harrowing%20loss%20of%20life.%20In%20our%20grief%2C%20we%20are%20horrified%20to%20see%20the%20fight%20against%20antisemitism%20weaponised%20as%20a%20pretext%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fdamning-evidence-of-war-crimes-as-israeli-attacks-wipe-out-entire-families-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%3Ewar%20crimes%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20stated%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjewishcurrents.org%2Fa-textbook-case-of-genocide%5C%22%3Egenocidal%20intent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAntisemitism%20is%20an%20excruciatingly%20painful%20part%20of%20our%20community%E2%80%99s%20past%20and%20present.%20Our%20families%20have%20escaped%20wars%2C%20harassment%2C%20pogroms%2C%20and%20concentration%20camps.%20We%20have%20studied%20the%20long%20histories%20of%20persecution%20and%20violence%20against%20Jews%2C%20and%20we%20take%20seriously%20the%20ongoing%20antisemitism%20that%20jeopardises%20the%20safety%20of%20Jews%20around%20the%20world.%20This%20October%20just%20marked%20the%20five-year%20anniversary%20of%20the%20worst%20antisemitic%20attack%20ever%20committed%20in%20the%20United%20States%3A%20the%20eleven%20worshipers%20at%20Tree%20of%20Life%20%E2%80%93%20Or%20L%E2%80%99Simcha%20in%20Pittsburgh%2C%20who%20were%20murdered%20by%20a%20gunman%20who%20espoused%20conspiracy%20theories%20that%20blamed%20Jews%20for%20the%20arrival%20of%20Central%20American%20migrants%2C%20and%20in%20so%20doing%2C%20dehumanised%20both%20groups.%20We%20reject%20antisemitism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%20including%20when%20it%20masquerades%20as%20criticism%20of%20Zionism%20or%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20policies.%20We%20also%20recognise%20that%2C%20as%20journalist%20Peter%20Beinart%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforward.com%2Fopinion%2F419988%2Fdebunking-the-myth-that-anti-zionism-is-anti-semitic%2F%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202019%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnti-Zionism%20is%20not%20inherently%20antisemitic%E2%80%94and%20claiming%20it%20is%20uses%20Jewish%20suffering%20to%20erase%20Palestinian%20experience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20find%20this%20rhetorical%20tactic%20antithetical%20to%20Jewish%20values%2C%20which%20teach%20us%20to%20repair%20the%20world%2C%20question%20authority%2C%20and%20champion%20the%20oppressed%20over%20the%20oppressor.%20It%20is%20precisely%20because%20of%20the%20painful%20history%20of%20antisemitism%20and%20lessons%20of%20Jewish%20texts%20that%20we%20advocate%20for%20the%20dignity%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20We%20refuse%20the%20false%20choice%20between%20Jewish%20safety%20and%20Palestinian%20freedom%3B%20between%20Jewish%20identity%20and%20ending%20the%20oppression%20of%20Palestinians.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20rights%20of%20Jews%20and%20Palestinians%20go%20hand-in-hand.%20The%20safety%20of%20each%20people%20depends%20on%20the%20other%E2%80%99s.%20We%20are%20certainly%20not%20the%20first%20to%20say%20so%2C%20and%20we%20admire%20those%20who%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2023%2F10%2F23%2Fnoy_katsman_hayim_katsman_israel_hostages%5C%22%3Ehave%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fisraeli-survivors-hamas-massacre-revenge%2F%5C%22%3Emodeled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0this%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenation.com%2Farticle%2Fworld%2Fpalestinians-and-israelis-will-not-be-safe-unless-all-are-safe%2F%5C%22%3Eline%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjewishcurrents.org%2Fdispatches-from-gaza%5C%22%3Ethinking%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20wake%20of%20so%20much%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20understand%20how%20antisemitism%20and%20criticism%20of%20Israel%20or%20Zionism%20have%20been%20conflated.%20For%20years%2C%20dozens%20of%20countries%20have%20upheld%20the%20International%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Alliance%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.holocaustremembrance.com%2Fresources%2Fworking-definitions-charters%2Fworking-definition-antisemitism%5C%22%3Eworking%20definition%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20antisemitism.%20Most%20of%20its%20eleven%20examples%20of%20antisemitism%20regard%20comments%20on%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%2C%20with%20some%20open%20to%20interpretation%20enough%20that%20they%20limit%20the%20scope%20of%20acceptable%20critique.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20Anti-Defamation%20League%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adl.org%2Fresources%2Fbackgrounder%2Fanti-zionism%5C%22%3Eclassifies%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Anti-Zionism%20as%20antisemitism%2C%20despite%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjewishcurrents.org%2Fadl-staffers-dissented-after-ceo-compared-palestinian-rights-groups-to-right-wing-extremists-leaked-audio-reveals%5C%22%3Emisgivings%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20many%20of%20its%20own%20experts.%20These%20definitions%20have%20scaffolded%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20deepening%20relationships%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fantisemitic-far-right-israel-orban%2F%5C%22%3Efar-right%2C%20antisemitic%20political%20forces%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20Hungary%20to%20Poland%20to%20the%20United%20States%20and%20beyond%E2%80%94endangering%20Jews%20in%20diaspora.%20To%20counter%20these%20sweeping%20definitions%2C%20a%20group%20of%20scholars%20of%20antisemitism%20published%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjerusalemdeclaration.org%2F%5C%22%3EJerusalem%20Declaration%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202020%2C%20offering%20more%20specific%20guidelines%20for%20identifying%20antisemitism%20and%20distinguishing%20it%20from%20criticism%20and%20debate%20around%20Israel%20and%20Zionism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp