%20calls%2C%20found%20the%20body%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20she%20was%20attacked%20as%20she%20was%20entering%20her%20house%20and%20her%20throat%20was%20slit.%20She%20was%20also%20stabbed%20multiple%20times.%20The%20attacker%20apparently%20dragged%20her%20body%20inside%20the%20house%20before%20escaping.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20suspected%20the%20killer%20was%20known%20to%20Prathima.%20Also%2C%20there%20was%20no%20sign%20of%20robbery.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathima's%20driver%2C%20whose%20phone%20had%20been%20switched%20off%2C%20was%20arrested%20this%20morning.%20Kiran%2C%2032%2C%20had%20been%20sacked%20by%20her%2010%20days%20ago.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20the%20geologist%20was%20dropped%20home%20by%20a%20new%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathima%2C%20who%20completed%20her%20Masters%20from%20Kuvempu%20University%20in%20Shivamogga%2C%20joined%20the%20Mines%20and%20Geology%20Department%20as%20a%20geologist%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20worked%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Ramnagara%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20had%20specialised%20in%20rural%20areas.%20A%20year%20ago%2C%20she%20was%20promoted%20to%20senior%20geologist%20and%20was%20appointed%20Deputy%20Director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20recently%20carried%20out%20a%20raid%20at%20an%20illegal%20quarry%2C%20reporting%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%2C%20after%20which%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20and%20three%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathima%20had%20lived%20alone%20in%20a%20double-storied%20independent%20house%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699271160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4jfrl9u_bengaluru-woman-official-murdered-_625x300_05_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-was-prathima-ks-government-officer-murdered-at-bengaluru-home-4550453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Ka