%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESori%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%202014%20from%20the%20local%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebazaar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20police%20suddenly%20turned%20up%20there%20and%20arrested%20me%20and%20claimed%20that%20I%20was%20helping%20Naxalis%20as%20an%20informer.%20I%20was%20doing%20no%20such%20thing%20but%20they%20did%20not%20listen%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20terms%20%E2%80%98Naxali%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Naxal%E2%80%99%20are%20used%20interchangeably%20to%20mean%20%E2%80%98Maoists%E2%80%99%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20case%20dragged%20on%20for%20years%20in%20court%20as%20witnesses%2C%20who%20he%20said%20were%20largely%20villagers%20from%20Chindgur%20and%20police%20officials%2C%20rarely%20turned%20up%20to%20provide%20any%20evidence%20of%20his%20involvement%20with%20Maoists%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20was%20Naxali%20then%20something%20would%20come%20out%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20But%20nothing%20ever%20came%20out%20and%20finally%20the%20case%20was%20dismissed%20and%20I%20was%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Sori%20went%20to%20jail%20his%20daughter%20was%20just%20born.%20Nine%20years%20on%2C%20Sori%20has%20met%20his%20daughter%20twice%20after%20being%20released%20from%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20332px)%2085vw%2C%20332px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22332%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683742%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShyam%20Kavasi%20who%20left%20Chandameta%20for%20nine%20years%20with%20his%20family%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20Maoists.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20whole%20youth%20has%20been%20wasted%20in%20jail.%20Now%20I%20want%20to%20work%20hard%20on%20my%20farm%20to%20educate%20my%20daughter.%20This%20is%20like%20a%20new%20birth%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20what%20he%20feels%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20his%20own%20village%2C%20Sori%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20they%20(police%20and%20security%20forces)%20would%20look%20at%20us%20with%20suspicion%2C%20now%20they%20are%20urging%20us%20to%20go%20and%20vote.%20What%20can%20I%20say%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20shadow%20on%20Chandameta%E2%80%99s%20development%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Sori%20has%20been%20released%2C%20about%2010%20other%20villagers%20who%20were%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20aids%20to%20the%20Maoists%20like%20him%2C%20are%20still%20lodged%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20those%20who%20are%20still%20in%20jail%20to%20be%20released%20as%20early%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2021-year-old%20Shyam%20Kavasi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20said%20that%20his%20family%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20village%20for%20nine%20years%20at%20the%20height%20of%20Maoist%20activities%20in%20the%20area%20and%20only%20returned%20to%20the%20village%20two%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20CRPF%20camp%20was%20set%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20left%20out%20of%20fear.%20Even%20if%20we%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bazaar%20we%20had%20to%20get%20their%20permission.%20If%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20permission%20they%20would%20accuse%20us%20of%20going%20to%20meet%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20and%20four%20others%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20in%20the%20village%20who%20have%20studied%20till%20Class%2012.%20With%20basic%20amenities%20now%20available%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Kavasi%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20village%20to%20develop%20like%20other%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CElectricity%20has%20just%20come%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20month%20but%20not%20to%20the%20entire%20village%20yet.%20One%20para%20still%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20electricity.%20When%20we%20see%20other%20villages%20they%20are%20well%20developed%2C%20we%20also%20want%20our%20village%20to%20be%20developed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20had%20developed%20our%20village%20earlier%20then%20this%20place%20would%20not%20have%20become%20Naxal%20dominated.%20Several%20villagers%20have%20been%20killed.%20Many%20villagers%20would%20see%20police%20and%20run%20away%20and%20the%20police%20would%20shoot%20them%20out%20of%20suspicion.%20I%20know%20of%20at%20least%20two%20such%20cases.%20The%20villagers%20have%20lost%20out%20between%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20Maoists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarish%20Mandavi%2C%2021%2C%20says%20that%20villagers%20often%20did%20not%20have%20any%20option%20but%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20come%20and%20point%20a%20gun%20to%20our%20heads%20and%20ask%20us%20for%20rice%2C%20dal%20and%20other%20rations%20or%20to%20cook%20food%20for%20them.%20We%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20do%20as%20they%20said%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMandavi%20who%20has%20studied%20till%20Class%205%20say%20that%20his%20father%20left%20him%20and%20his%20mother%20and%20two%20sisters%20in%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20live%20under%20this%20kind%20of%20pressure%20anymore.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20leaving%20this%20village.%20I%20always%20thought%20that%20if%20I%20have%20to%20die%20then%20I%20will%20die%20here%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20villagers%20in%20Chandameta%20are%20still%20involved%20with%20Maoists%2C%20say%20current%20residents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20said%20that%20the%20Maoists%20would%20hold%20political%20discussions%20in%20the%20village%20and%20convince%20the%20villagers%20about%20not%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20like%20political%20parties%20hold%20rallies%20in%20which%20they%20give%20speeches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20had%20brought%20development%20earlier%20then%20maybe%20Naxals%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20so%20entrenched%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06165057%2FVoter-information-painted-on-Chandameta