%20ill%20and%20needed%20hospital%20care%20we%20would%20send%20them%20to%20the%20nearby%20hospitals.%20None%20of%20them%20had%20Aadhaar%20cards%20or%20voter%20ID%20cards.%20We%20got%20that%20done%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20taken%20time%20but%20now%20the%20villagers%20have%20come%20to%20trust%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVillagers%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20they%20are%20keen%20to%20work%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20other%20youth%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Kavasi%20is%20trying%20to%20organise%20the%20villagers%20as%20a%20collective%20to%20bring%20more%20development%20to%20the%20village.%20Government%20officials%20including%20the%20Jagdalpur%20collector%20have%20visited%20the%20village%20a%20few%20times%20recently%20and%20promised%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%20so%20we%20can%20make%20more%20demands%20to%20the%20government%20and%20bring%20more%20developmental%20work%20here.%20Development%20has%20come%20so%20suddenly%20here%20with%20roads%2C%20electricity%20that%20villagers%20themselves%20cannot%20understand%20how%20these%20things%20have%20happened%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kavasi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699270153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164948%2FElectricity-lines-in-Chandameta-village.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20villagers%20in%20Chandameta%20had%20to%20walk%20about%206%20kilometres%20to%20Chindgur%20to%20cast%20their%20votes.%20As%20many%20as%20337%20voters%20are%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20village%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BBC%20reports%20from%20southern%20Gaza%20after%20'intense'%20air%20strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699270071000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3946%2Fproduction%2F_131626641_p0gqzg9m.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67333418%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'We%20are%20struggling%20to%20get%20credible%20information'%2C%20says%20the%20BBC's%20Rushdi%20Abualouf.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-middle-east-67333418%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Days%20After%20157%20Killed%20In%20Strong%20Earthquake%2C%20Another%20One%20Hits%20Nepal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENepal%20was%20hit%20by%20a%205.6%20magnitude%20earthquake%20today%2C%20days%20after%20157%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20injured%20when%20a%20strong%20quake%20struck%20the%20Himalayan%20country.%20The%20tremors%20were%20felt%20in%20neighbouring%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20earthquake%20this%20week%20occurred%20on%20Friday%20with%20a%20magnitude%206.4%2C%20Nepal's%20National%20Seismological%20Centre%20said.%20The%20German%20Research%20Centre%20for%20Geosciences%20measured%20the%20quake%20at%205.7%2C%20downgrading%20it%20from%206.2%2C%20while%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20pegged%20it%20at%205.6.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20count%20in%20Friday's%20earthquake%20in%20Jajarkot%20could%20rise%2C%20officials%20feared%2C%20as%20they%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20contact%20in%20the%20hilly%20area%20near%20the%20epicentre%2C%20some%20500%20km%20(300%20miles)%20west%20of%20the%20capital%20Kathmandu%2C%20where%20tremors%20were%20also%20felt.%20The%20district%20has%20a%20population%20of%20190%2C000%20with%20villages%20scattered%20in%20remote%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20was%20also%20blocked%20by%20landslides%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20earthquake%2C%20which%20hit%20the%20roads%20to%20reach%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20Nepal%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20quake%2C%20thousands%20of%20buildings%20in%20Jajarkot%20and%20neighbouring%20Rukum%20West%20district%20have%20collapsed%20or%20developed%20cracks%20making%20them%20uninhabitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20said%20they%20heard%20the%20loud%20noises%20of%20collapsing%20buildings%20soon%20after%20the%20quake%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20footage%20showed%20crumbled%20facades%20of%20multi-storied%20brick%20houses%2C%20with%20large%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20scattered.%20Videos%20on%20X%20showed%20people%20running%20into%20the%20street%20as%20some%20buildings%20were%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20earthquake%20was%20the%20deadliest%20since%202015%20when%20about%209%2C000%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20earthquakes%20in%20Nepal.%20Whole%20towns%2C%20centuries-old%20temples%20and%20other%20historic%20sites%20were%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20then%2C%20with%20more%20than%20a%20million%20houses%20destroyed%2C%20at%20a%20cost%20to%20the%20economy%20of%20%246%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699270020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fiaqmgucs_nepal-earthquake-reuters_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdays-after-157-killed-in-strong-earthquake-another-one-hits-nepal-4550354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nepal%20was%20hit%20by%20a%205.6%20magnitude%20earthquake%20today%2C%20days%20after%20157%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20injured%20when%20a%20strong%20quake%20struck%20the%20Hi