s%20no%20different%20after%20India's%20mammoth%20243-run%20victory%20over%20South%20Africa%20at%20the%20iconic%20Eden%20Gardens%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20won%20the%20Fielder%20of%20the%20Match%20medal%20in%20Eden%20Gardens%20after%20India%20hammered%20South%20Africa%20by%20243%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20impressed%20with%20his%20sharp%20fielding%20skills%20and%20an%20attacking%20start%20with%20bat%20which%20gave%20the%20hosts%20a%20solid%20state%20in%20their%20innings.%20He%20played%20stunning%20innings%20of%2040%20runs%20in%2024%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Rohit%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20medal%20winner%2C%20India%20opener%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20batter%20Ishan%20Kishan%20went%20over%20to%20the%20India%20captain%20and%20congratulated%20him.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20presented%20India's%20skipper%20with%20a%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20beauty%20of%20our%20team%20is%20that%20we%20just%20fly%20on%20the%20field%20but%20also%20we%20don't%20field%20with%20the%20hands%20but%20it%20is%20with%20a%20genuine%20commitment%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20today.%20This%20reminds%20me%20of%20a%20simple%20and%20most%20important%20quote%20I%20feel%20is%20that%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20whole%20team%20is%20each%20member.%20We%20have%20a%20new%20entry%20today.%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20did%20show%20that%20his%20quickness%20and%20his%20effort%20on%20the%20field%20was%20fantastic%2C%26quot%3B%20Dilip%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzSlm4qyJ-B%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3