3%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Frohit-sharma-in-splits-before-best-fielder-announcement-sends-team-india-berserk-watch-4549124%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Frohit-sharma-in-splits-before-best-fielder-announcement-sends-team-india-berserk-watch-4549124%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Frohit-sharma-in-splits-before-best-fielder-announcement-sends-team-india-berserk-watch-4549124%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20Driver%2C%2070%2C%20Earns%20Rs%2023%20Lakh%20By%20Cancelling%20Rides%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20Love%20It%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2070-year-old%20Uber%20driver%20from%20North%20Carolina%2C%20United%20States%2C%20earned%20over%20%2428%2C000%20(Rs%2023.3%20lakhs)%20by%20cancelling%20more%20than%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20trips%20in%20a%20year.%20The%20driver%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20pseudonym%20%26quot%3BBill%26quot%3B%20shared%20that%20he%20accepted%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20requests%20and%20undertook%20roughly%201%2C500%20trips%20in%202022%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fa-70-year-old-uber-driver-explains-how-canceling-over-30-of-his-rides-and-only-driving-during-busy-periods-have-helped-boost-his-pay%2Farticleshow%2F104895614.cms%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20retired%20six%20years%20ago%20and%20started%20working%20part-time%20at%20the%20ride-hailing%20platform%20to%20earn%20extra%20income.%20However%2C%20he%20does%20not%20accept%20just%20any%20ride%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20trips%20are%20worth%20his%20time.%20Bill%20stated%20that%20surge%20pricing%20in%20his%20area%20has%20reduced%20and%20this%20has%20%26quot%3Bmade%20him%20decrease%20his%20driving%20hours%26quot%3B.%20The%20man%20used%20to%20work%2040%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20but%20now%20that%20the%20surge%20has%20reduced%2C%20he%20now%20works%2030%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20saying%20no.%20I%20don't%20work%20unless%20we%20have%20a%20surge.%26quot%3B%20Bill%20stated%20that%20he%20and%20other%20drivers%20were%20able%20to%20make%20up%20to%20%2450%20per%20hour%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20when%20some%20of%20the%20drivers%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20driving%20because%20of%20health%20concerns.%20However%2C%20now%2C%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20drivers%2C%20he%20only%20makes%20%2415%20to%20%2420%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bill%20said%20that%20he%20employs%20several%20strategies%20to%20make%20decent%20money.%20He%20places%20himself%20in%20locations%20like%20airports%20and%20bars%20during%20rush%20hours%20between%2010%3A00%20pm%20to%202%3A30%20am%20on%20Fridays%20and%20Saturdays%20which%20helps%20with%20surge%20pricing.%20He%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20plane%20lands%20and%20people%20request%20Ubers%20the%20price%20jumps%20drastically.%20A%2020-minute%20ride%20goes%20from%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20to%20%2440%20and%20sometimes%20%2450.%20The%20driver%20gets%20just%20short%20of%2050%20per%20cent%20so%20a%2035-minute%20ride%20can%20get%20you%20%2430%20to%20%2460.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2070-year-old%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20avoids%20%26quot%3Bone-way%20rides%26quot%3B.%20Bill%20recalled%20a%20trip%20where%20he%20took%20a%20customer%20to%20a%20remote%20location%2C%20approximately%20two%20hours%20drive%20from%20his%20city.%20Even%20though%20he%20received%20%2427%20for%20the%20journey%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20drive%20%26quot%3Bfor%20free%26quot%3B%20since%20there%20were%20no%20customers%20on%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20strategies%20do%20come%20with%20some%20dangers.%20According%20to%20Uber%2C%20denying%20or%20cancelling%20a%20trip%20because%20of%20the%20driver's%20destination%20may%20result%20in%20the%20driver%20losing%20access%20to%20their%20account.%20Although%20Bill%20hasn't%20experienced%20it%20himself%2C%20he%20has%20heard%20of%20drivers%20being%20barred%20from%20airport%20pickups%20for%20cancelling%20long%20trips.%20Drivers%20who%20cancel%20more%20frequently%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20also%20lose%20access%20to%20the%20company's%20rewards%20programme%20which%20has%20perks%20like%20discounts%20at%20specific%20petrol%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bill%20intends%20to%20stick%20to%20his%20game%20plan%20for%20the%20time%20being%20and%20only%20drive%20when%20he%20believes%20it%20will%20be%20beneficial.%20He%20claimed%20that%20not%20depending%20on%20Uber%20for%20income%20is%20beneficial%20for%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20drive%20to%20get%20out%20and%20don't%20need%20the%20money.%20I%20love%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699261200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fp6kv1odg_uber-generic-reuters_625x300_06_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-driver-70-earns-rs-23-crore-by-cancelling-rides-i-love-it-4549680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20retired%20six%20years%20ago%20and%20started%20working%20part-time%20at%20the%20ride-hailing%20platform%20to%20earn%20extra%20income.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-driver-70-earns-rs-23-crore-by-cancelling-rides-i-love-it-4549680%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-driver-70-earns-rs-23-crore-by-cancelling-rides-i-love-it-4549680%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-driver-70-earns-rs-23-crore-by-cancelling-rides-i-love-it-4549680%2Famp%2F1%22