3F%20It's%20a%20war%20cry%20that%20seems%20to%20reverberate%20from%20a%20different%20era%2C%20one%20that%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20future%20that%20once%20seemed%20promised%20-%20a%20future%20where%20work%20serves%20life%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhay%20tells%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20while%20I%20can%20take%20a%20break%2C%20many%20of%20my%20college%20friends%20are%20still%20coding%20for%20giants%20like%20Infosys%20and%20Wipro%3F%20Their%20salaries%20have%20been%20stagnant%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20It's%20disheartening%20to%20see%20the%20fresher's%20paychecks%20barely%20budge%20while%20the%20CXOs'%20compensation%20soars%20to%20new%20heights%20with%20each%20passing%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Century's%20Leap%20Backward%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbhay's%20need%20for%20a%20break%20from%20the%20relentless%20tech%20world%20reminds%20us%20of%20past%20efforts%20to%20balance%20work%20and%20life%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspeninstitute.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Ffiles%2Fcontent%2Fupload%2FIntro_and_Section_I.pdf%5C%22%3EKeynes'%20dream%20of%20a%20short%20work%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ford's%20bold%20move%20to%20give%20workers%20weekends%20off.%20These%20were%20significant%20steps%20back%20then%20aimed%20at%20making%20work%20more%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKeynes'%201930%20vision%20of%20a%2015-hour%20work%20week%2C%20a%20future%20where%20technology%20liberates%20rather%20than%20enslaves%2C%20starkly%20contrasts%20with%20the%20present%20reality%2C%20where%20the%20measure%20of%20one's%20life%20is%20too%20often%20the%20measure%20of%20one's%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%201922%2C%20the%20Ford%20Motor%20Company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1922%2F03%2F25%2Farchives%2F5day-40hour-week-for-ford-employes-new-permanent-working-policy.html%5C%22%3Emade%20headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20commitment%20to%20a%20five-day%20workweek%2C%20a%20revolutionary%20concept%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20man%20needs%20more%20than%20one%20day%20a%20week%20for%20rest%20and%20recreation%2C%26quot%3B%20Edsel%20Ford%20proclaimed%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bideal%20home%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECloser%20to%20home%2C%20there's%20the%20poignant%20Bollywood%20adage%20from%20'Anand'%3A%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3BBabu%20Moshai%2C%20Zindagi%20badi%20honi%20chahiye%2C%20lambi%20nahi...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Life%20should%20be%20large%2C%20not%20necessarily%20long)%2C%20which%20underscores%20the%20quest%20for%20a%20meaningful%20existence%20over%20mere%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20'Anand's'%20profound%20insight%20that%20life's%20value%20is%20in%20its%20richness%2C%20not%20its%20duration%2C%20we%20find%20a%20stark%20contrast%20in%20industry%20veterans%20like%20Sunil%20Shetty%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsuniel-shetty_once-again-the-debate-around-work-life-balance-activity-7125038780520026112-D2_4%5C%22%3Eechoes%20a%20sentiment%20of%20relentless%20pursuit%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20life's%20breadth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrities%20such%20as%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Ratan%20Tata%20that%20Shetty%20mentions%20are%20indeed%20paragons%20of%20their%20fields%2C%20but%20their%20stories%20are%20not%20just%20about%20hours%20worked.%20They%20are%20about%20passion%2C%20talent%2C%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20hard%20work%20-%20but%20also%20about%20the%20support%20systems%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20sometimes%20sheer%20luck%20that%20contribute%20to%20such%20exceptional%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20we%20expect%2C%20or%20even%20demand%2C%20this%20level%20of%20commitment%20from%20everyone%2C%20or%20does%20it%20risk%20setting%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Assembly%20Line%20Mentality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20where%20machines%20are%20poised%20to%20relieve%20us%20of%20repetitive%20tasks%2C%20the%20call%20for%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%20from%20industry%20veterans%20like%20Narayana%20Murthy%20seems%20out%20of%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20longer%20hours%20by%20industry%20stalwarts%20like%20Murthy%20echoes%20a%20bygone%20era-an%20era%20we%20moved%20away%20from%20for%20our%20collective%20well-being.%20The%20assembly%20line%20mentality%20prioritizes%20quantity%20and%20efficiency%2C%20often%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20creativity%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20advancing%20or%20regressing%3F%20Can%20we%20aspire%20to%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20progress-one%20that%20doesn't%20equate%20worth%20with%20weariness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEncouraging%20every%20young%20individual%20to%20adopt%20this%20intense%2C%20hours-focused%20work%20ethic%20may%20not%20only%20be%20unrealistic%20but%20could%20also%20lead%20to%20burnout%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20innovation%20and%20creativity.%20It's%20crucial%20to%20recognize%20that%20different%20industries%2C%20roles%2C%20and%20individuals%20may%20require%20varied%20approaches%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20the%20debate%20over%20the%2070-hour%20work%20week%20is%20more%20than%20a%20question%20of%20productivity%20-%20it's%20a%20question%20of%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20AI%20can%20drive%20our%20cars%2C%20write%20our%20codes%2C%20and%20even%20create%20art%2C%20what%20is%20the%20role%20of%20the%20human%20professional%3F%20How%20do%20we%20navigate%20a%20landscape%20that%20is%20ever-changing%2C%20ever-evolving%2C%20and%20increasingly%20autonomous%3F%20These%20are%20not%20questions%20with%20easy%20answers%2C%20but%20they%20must%20be%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcademic%20Inferno%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20debate%20takes%20a%20grim%20turn%20when%20we%20examine%20the%20pressure%20cooker%20environment%20of%20India's%20competitive%20exams.%20The%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20academic%20excellence%20has%20pushed%20many%20to%20the%20brink%2C%20with%20Kota's%20coaching%20centres%20becoming%20a%20grim%20reminder%20of%20this%20epidemic.%20The%20crisis%20in%20our%20educational%20institutions%20is%20a%20microcosm%20of%20the%20larger%20issue%2C%20reflecting%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20equates%20success%20with%20long%20hours%20and%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20climate%2C%20the%20advocacy%20for%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%20seems%20not%20just%20out%20of%20touch%20but%20dangerously%20negligent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20of%20Kota%2C%20known%20as%20the%20coaching%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20this%20relentless%20pressure.%20Every%20year%2C%20thousands%20of%20students%20flock%20to%20the%20city%20with%20dreams%20of%20cracking%20the%20coveted%20exams.%20The%20NCRB%20data%20is%20alarming%2C%20with%20a%2070%25%20increase%20in%20student%20suicides%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20Kota%20alone%20witnessing%2024%20such%20tragedies%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20crisis%20doesn't%20end%20there.%20Even%20those%20who%20make%20it%20to%20the%20IITs%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20the%20pressures.%20Cases%20of%20suicides%20in%20these%20premier%20institutions%20are%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20with%20academic%20stress%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20belong%20being%20cited%20as%20the%20prime%20reasons.%20The%20competitive%20culture%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20adequate%20support%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20stigma%20around%20mental%20health%20are%20creating%20a%20perfect%20storm%2C%20pushing%20students%20to%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20spoke%20to%20an%20undergrad%20at%20one%20of%20the%20IITs%20and%20asked%20how%20he%20feels%20about%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20suicides.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20us%20can't%20bear%20the%20relentless%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20confided.%20%26quot%3BThe%20grind%20doesn't%20stop%20after%20you%20survive%20the%20gauntlet%20of%20the%20entrance%20exams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20excellence%20doesn't%20pause%20to%20catch%20its%20breath%3B%20it%20simply%20morphs%20into%20the%20next%20challenge%2C%20the%20next%20steep%20climb.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20these%20young%20minds%2C%20already%20forged%20in%20the%20crucible%20of%20academic%20rigour%2C%20stepping%20into%20a%20workplace%20that%20demands%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20reflect%20on%20these%20harrowing%20stories%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20draw%20parallels%20with%20the%20corporate%20world.%20The%2070-hour%20work%20week%2C%20the%20glorification%20of%20overwork%2C%20the%20assembly%20line%20mindset%20-%20a%20culture%20permeating%20every%20aspect%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20from%20education%20to%20employment.%20And%20it's%20leaving%20a%20trail%20of%20broken%20dreams%20and%20shattered%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErosion%20of%20Work%20Ethic%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20uproar%20over%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%20and%20the%20'moonlighting%20is%20a%20crime'%20stance%20not%20about%20the%20hours%20but%20about%20a%20commitment%20to%20work%20that%20is%20waning%3F%20Are%20we%20facing%20a%20crisis%20of%20commitment%20rather%20than%20a%20problem%20of%20overwork%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20I%20spent%20time%20in%20two%20long%20conversations%20trying%20to%20explore%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20coin.%20The%20first%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20start-up%20founder%2C%20had%20recently%20instituted%20a%20policy%20mandating%20a%20four-day%20physical%20office%20presence%2C%20a%20move%20that%20rippled%20with%20controversy.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20how%20tough%20it's%20become%20to%20extract%20work%20from%20the%20youth%3F%20They're%20touchy%2C%20tentative%2C%20and%20distracted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20confided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20CEO%20of%20a%20top%20talent%20firm%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20longer%20an%20HR%20or%20culture%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20fast%20becoming%20a%20core%20business%20concern.%20The%20questions%20of%20delegation%20and%20oversight%20have%20never%20been%20more%20pressing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20encounters%20left%20me%20wondering%20if%20the%20essence%20of%20Narayana%20Murthy's%2070-hour%20work%20week%20commentary%20was%20more%20about%20work%20ethic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECould%20there%20be%20merit%20in%20expecting%20a%20certain%20work%20ethic%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20hours%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20then%2C%20the%20uproar%20over%20Murthy's%20call%20to%20arms%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FRishad%2520Premji%2527s%2520staunch%2520stance%2520against%2520%2527moonlighting%2527%5C%22%3ERishad%20Premji's%20staunch%20stance%20against%20'moonlighting'%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20deeper%20issue.%20It's%20not%20merely%20about%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20clocked%20but%20about%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20reflection%20does%20not%20negate%20the%20concerns%20I've%20raised%20about%20the%20mental%20and%20emotional%20toll%20of%20overwork.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20compel%20us%20to%20consider%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20coin-a%20side%20where%20the%20discipline%20of%20work%20ethic%20is%20in%20jeopardy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20Large%2C%20Not%20Long%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20costs%20of%20this%20relentless%20push%3F%20The%20burnout%2C%20the%20mental%20health%20crises%2C%20the%20lost%20moments%20with%20family%20-%20aren't%20these%20just%20as%20important%20as%20the%20accolades%20and%20achievements%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20era%20where%20technology%20and%20AI%20are%20reshaping%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20work.%20The%20skills%20needed%20today%20are%20vastly%20different%20from%20those%20of%20the%20past.%20Does%20it%20make%20sense%20to%20adapt%20our%20work%20ethic%20to%20this%20new%20reality%20rather%20than%20cling%20to%20an%20outdated%20model%20that%20may%20no%20longer%20serve%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20scrutinize%20the%2070-hour%20work%20week%2C%20let's%20not%20mistake%20relentless%20toil%20for%20true%20achievement.%20'Anand'%20reminded%20us%20that%20a%20fulfilling%20life%20isn't%20measured%20in%20hours%20but%20in%20moments%20and%20connections.%20So%2C%20let's%20redefine%20success%20to%20mean%20more%20than%20career%20highs%20-%20let's%20include%20the%20health%20of%20our%20hearts%20and%20the%20joy%20in%20our%20journey.%20After%20all%2C%20it's%20the%20richness%20of%20our%20experiences%2C%20not%20the%20length%20of%20our%20workdays%2C%20that%20truly%20defines%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20FactorDaily.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699260000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6oo6pqpo_working-on-computer-unsplash-_625x300_06_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F70-hour-work-week-a-lesson-from-rajesh-khannas-anand-4549335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Let's%20redefine%20success%20to%20mean%20more%20than%20career%20highs%20-%20let's%20include%20the%20health%20of%20our%20hearts%20and%20the%20joy%20in%20our%20journey.%20After%20all%2C%20it's%20the%20richness%20of%20our%20experiences%2C%20not%20the%20length%20of%20our%20workdays%2C%20that%20truly%20defines%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F70-hour-work-week-a-lesson-from-rajesh-khannas-anand-4549335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sabyasachi%20Faces%20Backlash%20For%20Featuring%20''Unhappy''%20Models%20Without%20Bindi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20festive%20and%20wedding%20season