sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faverage-ryanair-fares-up-24-as-company-forecasts-record-profits-13001754%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faverage-ryanair-fares-up-24-as-company-forecasts-record-profits-13001754%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leaving%2C%20Staying%2C%20and%20Being%20Caged%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06110857%2Fsignal-2023-11-05-210917.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20article%20in%20a%20series%20from%20Israel-Palestine.%20Read%20the%20first%20article%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-diary-gaza-occupation%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20second%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwar-will-surely-bring-peace-this-time-notes-from-israel-palestine%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20October%2013%2C%20and%20Israel%20has%20ordered%20the%201.1%20million%20people%20living%20in%20the%20North%20of%20Gaza%20to%20evacuate%20to%20the%20South.%20Khalil%20and%20his%20family%20live%20in%20the%20North.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20friends%20who%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20Khalil%20are%20sending%20screenshots%20of%20their%20conversation%20with%20him%20on%20our%20group%20chat%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ER%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20just%20found%20out%20about%20the%20inhumane%20evacuation%20notice.%20Praying%20that%20you%20have%20a%20place%20to%20be%20and%20that%20you%20are%20being%20held%20by%20loved%20ones%20right%20now%20%3C%2Fem%3E%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%3A%3Cem%3E%20It%20is%20displacement%20and%20cleansing.%20It%20is%20a%20miracle%20that%20I%20could%20move%20South%2C%20but%20my%20sisters%20and%20grandmother%20are%20stuck%20there.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ER%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20am%20so%20so%20sorry.%20I%20am%20thinking%20and%20praying%20for%20them.%20It%20is%20a%20true%20miracle%20that%20you%20could%20move%20South.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20say%20except%20that%20I%20love%20you%20and%20you%20are%20a%20light%20in%20all%20of%20this%20darkness.%20I%20am%20in%20awe%20of%20you%20and%20your%20strength.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20believe%20you%20made%20it.%20I%20am%20thinking%20of%20you%20every%20moment%20%3C%2Fem%3E%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%3A%20%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomeone%20in%20the%20group%20chat%20asks%20if%20Khalil%20said%20anything%20else%20about%20his%20sisters%20and%20grandmother.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20move%20for%20fear%20of%20the%20bombings%20on%20the%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20texted%20another%20friend%2C%20%E2%80%9Capparently%2070%20people%20fleeing%20have%20been%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20in%20my%20room%20in%20Jerusalem%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20Old%20City%20from%20the%20window.%20Its%20walls%20look%20beautiful%20at%20night%20when%20it%20reflects%20the%20floodlights.%20People%20are%20saying%20that%20Israel%20is%20going%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20internet%20in%20Gaza%20tonight.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20want%20Khalil%E2%80%99s%20voice%20to%20reach%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20so%20I%20contact%20two%20reporters%20in%20the%20United%20States%20who%20work%20for%20major%20news%20organisations%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20reaching%20out%20to%20share%20a%20contact%20I%20have%20in%20Gaza%2C%20maybe%20you%20will%20be%20interested%20in%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20him%3F%20He%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20studies%20literature%2C%20and%20is%20an%20amazing%20human%20being.%20He%20has%20been%20running%20from%20the%20North%20to%20the%20South%2C%20and%20I%20am%20really%20scared%20about%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20never%20responded%2C%20and%20the%20other%20texted%20the%20following%20day%20that%20they%20were%20able%20to%20contact%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20doing%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20reporter%20said%20%E2%80%93%20which%20in%20the%20present%20context%20means%20bare%20survival.%20My%20friend%20tells%20me%20that%20she%20connected%20Khalil%20with%20the%20Associated%20Press.%20Now%20he%20is%20being%20quoted%20in%20a%20few%20of%20their%20news%20reports%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20orders%20the%20evacuation%20of%201.1%20million%20people%20from%20northern%20part%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20UN%20says%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-gaza-hamas-airstrikes-cabinet-beb1fa2b9e4ede6cf4568dd6c86ff11a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20flee%20because%20anywhere%20you%20go%2C%20you%20are%20bombed%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20neighbor%2C%20Khalil%20Abu%20Yahia%2C%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20miracle%20to%20survive%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%20forced%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20the%20airstrikes%20soared%2025%25%20in%20a%20day%2C%20reaching%20423%2C000%20out%20of%20a%20population%20of%202.3%20million%2C%20the%20U.N.%20said%20Thursday.%20Most%20crowded%20into%20U.N.-run%20schools.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELack%20of%20water%20worsens%20misery%20in%20besieged%20Gaza%20as%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20continue%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-gaza-hamas-water-4cc305b209437eec7235e975cf4c47d6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20besieged%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%99s%202.3%20million%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20clean%2C%20running%20water%20after%20Israel%20cut%20off%20water%20and%20electricity%20to%20the%20enclave%20as%20it%20intensifies%20its%20air%20attacks%20in%20response%20to%20a%20bloody%20Hamas%20attack%20last%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20in%20the%20stone%20ages%2C%E2%80%99%20said%2028-year-old%20Khalil%20Abu%20Yahia%20in%20the%20central%20town%20of%20Deir%20al-Balah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%20has%20a%20vast%20perspective%20and%20experience%20of%20war%20and%20colonialism%2C%20of%20resistance%20and%20nonviolence.%20But%20we%20have%20not%20created%20a%20world%20where%20voices%20like%20Khalil%20are%20heard%20easily%2C%20or%20heard%20at%20all.%20In%20the%20article%20above%2C%20he%20is%20quoted%20in%20passing.%20It%20could%20be%20worse%20for%20him%3B%20he%20could%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20statistic%20%E2%80%93%20the%20number%20of%20displaced%2C%20wounded%2C%20and%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20call%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20who%20is%20Jewish%2C%20lives%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20anti-occupation%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20dear%20friend%20of%20mine.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20him%20how%20he%20is%20doing%20and%20whether%20I%20should%20leave%20given%20the%20deteriorating%20situation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20is%20imminent.%20Once%20that%20happens%20Hezbollah%20might%20get%20involved%2C%20in%20which%20case%20there%20might%20be%20missiles%20striking%20all%20over%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20getting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20leave%2C%20you%20should%20probably%20leave.%20This%20is%20not%20going%20to%20end%20anytime%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwar-will-surely-bring-peace-this-time-notes-from-israel-palestine%5C%22%3EWar%20Will%20Surely%20Bring%20Peace%20This%20Time%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20feel%20quite%20shaken%20by%20his%20advice%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20uprooting%20my%20life%20here%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20He%20was%20traveling%20abroad%20when%20the%20war%20began%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20he%20returned%20to%20Israel%20today.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20kids%20who%20live%20abroad%20told%20me%20to%20not%20go%20back%20to%20Israel.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20come%20back%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20my%20grandchildren%20in%20Jerusalem.%20This%20is%20my%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20telling%20my%20Israeli-American%20friend%2C%20who%20is%20a%20secular%20Jew%2C%20about%20my%20conversation%20with%20the%20professor.%20My%20friend%20had%20to%20move%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Israel%20many%20years%20ago%20because%20of%20difficult%20family%20circumstances.%20%E2%80%9CI%20understood%20very%20quickly%20that%20my%20stay%20here%20must%20be%20temporary%2C%20that%20the%20occupation%20is%20evil%20but%20that%20I%20must%20be%20here%20now%20with%20my%20family.%20Everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20felt%20all%20these%20years%20about%20living%20here%20is%C2%A0%20coming%20to%20the%20surface%20at%20once%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandparents%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ecannot%20leave%20because%20they%20are%20too%20old%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20is%20not%20going%20to%20leave%20them%20here.%20What%20if%20the%20situation%20gets%20so%20bad%20that%20my%20family%20tells%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20go%20to%20the%20United%20States%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20myself%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20crying.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20I%20do%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks%20herself.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20maternal%20side%20of%20her%20family%20has%20lived%20here%20for%20at%20least%20seven%20generations%2C%20much%20before%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20was%20created%20in%201948.%20Her%20paternal%20family%20are%20Holocaust%20survivors%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20immigrated%20to%20Israel%20after%201948.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20invited%20friends%20for%20dinner.%20All%20my%20Jewish%20friends%20who%20oppose%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20are%20distressed%20by%20what%20they%20are%20seeing%20on%20social%20media%20and%20what%20people%20around%20them%20are%20saying.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20surrounded%20by%20pro-Israeli%20discourse.%20These%20friends%20are%20horrified%20and%20repulsed%20by%20how%20their%20family%2C%20friends%20and%20acquaintances%20are%20legitimising%20the%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20and%20dehumanising%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20toll%20from%20Gaza%20just%20surpassed%20Israeli%20deaths.%20Can%20we%20stop%20now%2C%20or%20is%20that%20not%20enough%3F%E2%80%9D%20posted%20an%20Israeli-American%20on%20Instagram.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20expect%20that%20people%20will%20understand%20that%20levying%20collective%20punishment%20on%20Gaza%20in%20response%20to%20what%20Hamas%20did%20is%20immoral%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20Israeli%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20can%20they%20at%20least%20see%20that%20this%20strategy%20has%20not%20made%20us%20safe%20over%20the%20decades%3F%E2%80%9D%20An%20Israeli-American%20friend%2C%20who%20refrains%20from%20posting%20anything%20on%20social%20media%2C%20had%20enough%20when%20her%20friends%20started%20posting%20about%20how%20Gazans%20are%20ungrateful%20that%20Israel%20provides%20them%20with%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20f**ing%20mansion%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20never%20had%20to%20worry%20about%20access%20to%20safe%20and%20clean%20drinking%20water%20whenever%20you%20want%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20you%20should%20take%20a%20second%20to%20think%20about%20your%20cold%20and%20removed%20statements%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20friends%20are%20more%20embedded%20in%20leftist%20circles%20than%20they%20are%20within%20Jewish%20ones%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20are%20infuriated%20that%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20left%E2%80%9D%20is%20demanding%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20room%20for%20mourning%20the%20Israeli%20civilians%20killed%20by%20Hamas%20militants.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Israeli%20friend%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20fed%20up%20with%20all%20the%20sheltered%20social%20justice%20warriors%20who%20read%20Franz%20Fanon%20and%20Edward%20Said%20once%20in%20their%20life%20and%20think%20that%20they%20have%20this%20whole%20conflict%20figured%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CHamas%E2%80%99%20goal%20is%20to%20replace%20a%20Jewish%20supremacist%20state%20with%20an%20Islamic%20theocracy%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20liberatory%20about%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%2C%20referring%20to%20people%20who%20see%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20actions%20as%20justifiable%20resistance%20against%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20What%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-what-its-like-to-be-a-palestinian-in-israel-prof-dalal-iriqat%5C%22%3EWhat%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20angry%20at%20what%20I%20am%20seeing%20on%20social%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20someone%20says%20at%20the%20dinner%20table.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20friend%20screams%20%E2%80%9CI%20fear%20the%20discourse!%E2%80%9D%20hysterically%20to%20make%20us%20all%20laugh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20text%20message%20on%20a%20group%20chat%2C%20addressed%20to%20Israeli%20and%20international%20activists%20who%20go%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20support%20Palestinian%20communities%20which%20are%20under%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20the%20army.%20These%20activists%20spend%20anywhere%20between%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20many%20weeks%20in%20these%20communities%2C%20helping%20Palestinians%20push%20back%20against%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20army.%20They%20use%20cameras%20and%20phones%20to%20film%20settlers%20when%20they%20come%20into%20these%20communities%20and%20intimidate%20or%20attack%20Palestinians%2C%20argue%20with%20them%2C%20and%20call%20the%20Israeli%20police.%20They%20film%20when%20the%20Israeli%20soldiers%20harass%20or%20use%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%2C%20hoping%20that%20the%20soldiers%20would%20moderate%20their%20behaviour%20because%20they%20are%20on%20camera%2C%20and%20any%20illegal%20behavior%20or%20arbitrary%20action%20by%20soldiers%20will%20be%20documented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20very%20alarmed%20on%20reading%20the%20text%20message%2C%20which%20says%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20has%20rapidly%20intensified.%20On%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20after%20two%20separate%20incidents%20of%20unprecedented%20violence%20and%20risk%20towards%20solidarity%20activists%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Wadi%20A-Siq%20and%20At-Tuwani%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20experienced%20Israeli%20activists%20had%20a%20meeting%20about%20the%20current%20situation%20and%20what%20it%20means%20for%20all%20of%20us%20as%20solidarity%20activists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20message%20then%20describes%20how%20in%20Wadi%20A-Siq%2C%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%20ziptied%20activists%20and%20held%20them%20captive%20for%20many%20hours%2C%20and%20took%20their%20phones%20and%20cameras%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20Settlers%20beating%20activists%20is%20common%2C%20but%20holding%20activists%20captive%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20for%20multiple%20hours%20nobody%20knew%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20captive%20activists.%20A%20settler-militia%20attacked%20At-Tuwani%20and%20opened%20fire%3B%20some%20activists%20were%20present%20there%20too.%20One%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20activists%20was%20shot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20that%20at%20this%20moment%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20actively%20or%20widely%20be%20inviting%20activists%20due%20to%20the%20current%20dangers.%20The%20drive%20down%20can%20be%20dangerous%2C%20and%20in%20the%20field%2C%20settlers%20and%20military%20(which%2C%20especially%20now%2C%20are%20indistinguishable%20because%20settlers%20are%20wearing%20army%20uniforms)%20are%20very%20clearly%20ready%20with%20their%20fingers%20on%20the%20trigger.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinians%20from%20this%20region%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20which%20is%20called%20Masafar%20Yatta%20or%20South%20Hebron%20Hills%2C%20were%20describing%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20from%20the%20day%20the%20war%20began.%20But%20I%20am%20still%20shocked%20after%20reading%20the%20text%20messages%20because%20these%20activists%20making%20such%20a%20decision%20feels%20unprecedented.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20reaffirmation%20of%20how%20bad%20things%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faman-abhishek%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAman%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Abhishek%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20PhD%20student%20in%20media%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%2C%20USA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699250404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06110857%2Fsignal-2023-11-05-210917.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnotes-from-israel-palestine-gaza-messages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20read%20of%20my%20friend%20Khalil%2C%20who%20has%20moved%20to%20south%20Gaza%20and%20is%20quoted%20in%20passing%20in%20news%20reports.%20It%20could%20be%20worse%20for%20him%3B%20he%20could%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20statistic%20%E2%80%93%20the%20number%20of%20displaced%2C%20wounded%2C%20and%20dead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnotes-from-israel-palestine-gaza-messages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leaving%2C%20Staying%2C%20and%20Being%20Caged%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06110857%2Fsignal-2023-11-05-210917.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20article%20in%20a%20series%20from%20Israel-Palestine.%20Read%20the%20first%20article%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-diary-gaza-occupation%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20second%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwar-will-surely-bring-peace-this-time-notes-from-israel-palestine%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20October%2013%2C%20and%20Israel%20has%20ordered%20the%201.1%20million%20people%20living%20in%20the%20North%20of%20Gaza%20to%20evacuate%20to%20the%20South.%20Khalil%20and%20his%20family%20live%20in%20the%20North.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20friends%20who%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20Khalil%20are%20sending%20screenshots%20of%20their%20conversation%20with%20him%20on%20our%20group%20chat%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ER%3A%20I%20just%20found%20out%20about%20the%20inhumane%20evacuation%20notice.%20Praying%20that%20you%20have%20a%20place%20to%20be%20and%20that%20you%20are%20being%20held%20by%20loved%20ones%20right%20now%20%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%3A%20It%20is%20displacement%20and%20cleansing.%20It%20is%20a%20miracle%20that%20I%20could%20move%20South%2C%20but%20my%20sisters%20and%20grandmother%20are%20stuck%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ER%3A%20I%20am%20so%20so%20sorry.%20I%20am%20thinking%20and%20praying%20for%20them.%20It%20is%20a%20true%20miracle%20that%20you%20could%20move%20South.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20say%20except%20that%20I%20love%20you%20and%20you%20are%20a%20light%20in%20all%20of%20this%20darkness.%20I%20am%20in%20awe%20of%20you%20and%20your%20strength.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20believe%20you%20made%20it.%20I%20am%20thinking%20of%20you%20every%20moment%20%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%3A%20%F0%9F%A4%8D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomeone%20in%20the%20group%20chat%20asks%20if%20Khalil%20said%20anything%20else%20about%20his%20sisters%20and%20grandmother.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20move%20for%20fear%20of%20the%20bombings%20on%20the%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20texted%20another%20friend%2C%20%E2%80%9Capparently%2070%20people%20fleeing%20have%20been%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20in%20my%20room%20in%20Jerusalem%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20Old%20City%20from%20the%20window.%20Its%20walls%20look%20beautiful%20at%20night%20when%20it%20reflects%20the%20floodlights.%20People%20are%20saying%20that%20Israel%20is%20going%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20internet%20in%20Gaza%20tonight.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20want%20Khalil%E2%80%99s%20voice%20to%20reach%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20so%20I%20contact%20two%20reporters%20in%20the%20United%20States%20who%20work%20for%20major%20news%20organisations%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20reaching%20out%20to%20share%20a%20contact%20I%20have%20in%20Gaza%2C%20maybe%20you%20will%20be%20interested%20in%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20him%3F%20He%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20studies%20literature%2C%20and%20is%20an%20amazing%20human%20being.%20He%20has%20been%20running%20from%20the%20North%20to%20the%20South%2C%20and%20I%20am%20really%20scared%20about%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20never%20responded%2C%20and%20the%20other%20texted%20the%20following%20day%20that%20they%20were%20able%20to%20contact%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20doing%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20reporter%20said%20%E2%80%93%20which%20in%20the%20present%20context%20means%20bare%20survival.%20My%20friend%20tells%20me%20that%20she%20connected%20Khalil%20with%20the%20Associated%20Press.%20Now%20he%20is%20being%20quoted%20in%20a%20few%20of%20their%20news%20reports%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20orders%20the%20evacuation%20of%201.1%20million%20people%20from%20northern%20part%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20UN%20says%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-gaza-hamas-airstrikes-cabinet-beb1fa2b9e4ede6cf4568dd6c86ff11a%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20flee%20because%20anywhere%20you%20go%2C%20you%20are%20bombed%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20neighbor%2C%20Khalil%20Abu%20Yahia%2C%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20miracle%20to%20survive%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%20forced%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20the%20airstrikes%20soared%2025%25%20in%20a%20day%2C%20reaching%20423%2C000%20out%20of%20a%20population%20of%202.3%20million%2C%20the%20U.N.%20said%20Thursday.%20Most%20crowded%20into%20U.N.-run%20schools.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELack%20of%20water%20worsens%20misery%20in%20besieged%20Gaza%20as%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20continue%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-gaza-hamas-water-4cc305b209437eec7235e975cf4c47d6%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20besieged%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%99s%202.3%20million%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20clean%2C%20running%20water%20after%20Israel%20cut%20off%20water%20and%20electricity%20to%20the%20enclave%20as%20it%20intensifies%20its%20air%20attacks%20in%20response%20to%20a%20bloody%20Hamas%20attack%20last%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20in%20the%20stone%20ages%2C%E2%80%99%20said%2028-year-old%20Khalil%20Abu%20Yahia%20in%20the%20central%20town%20of%20Deir%20al-Balah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalil%20has%20a%20vast%20perspective%20and%20experience%20of%20war%20and%20colonialism%2C%20of%20resistance%20and%20nonviolence.%20But%20we%20have%20not%20created%20a%20world%20where%20voices%20like%20Khalil%20are%20heard%20easily%2C%20or%20heard%20at%20all.%20In%20the%20article%20above%2C%20he%20is%20quoted%20in%20passing.%20It%20could%20be%20worse%20for%20him%3B%20he%20could%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20statistic%20%E2%80%93%20the%20number%20of%20displaced%2C%20wounded%2C%20and%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20call%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20who%20is%20Jewish%2C%20lives%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20anti-occupation%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20dear%20friend%20of%20mine.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20him%20how%20he%20is%20doing%20and%20whether%20I%20should%20leave%20given%20the%20deteriorating%20situation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20is%20imminent.%20Once%20that%20happens%20Hezbollah%20might%20get%20involved%2C%20in%20which%20case%20there%20might%20be%20missiles%20striking%20all%20over%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20getting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20leave%2C%20you%20should%20probably%20leave.%20This%20is%20not%20going%20to%20end%20anytime%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwar-will-surely-bring-peace-this-time-notes-from-israel-palestine%5C%22%3EWar%20Will%20Surely%20Bring%20Peace%20This%20Time%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20feel%20quite%20shaken%20by%20his%20advice%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20uprooting%20my%20life%20here%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20He%20was%20traveling%20abroad%20when%20the%20war%20began%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20he%20returned%20to%20Israel%20today.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20kids%20who%20live%20abroad%20told%20me%20to%20not%20go%20back%20to%20Israel.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20come%20back%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20my%20grandchildren%20in%20Jerusalem.%20This%20is%20my%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20telling%20my%20Israeli-American%20friend%2C%20who%20is%20a%20secular%20Jew%2C%20about%20my%20conversation%20with%20the%20professor.%20My%20friend%20had%20to%20move%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Israel%20many%20years%20ago%20because%20of%20difficult%20family%20circumstances.%20%E2%80%9CI%20understood%20very%20quickly%20that%20my%20stay%20here%20must%20be%20temporary%2C%20that%20the%20occupation%20is%20evil%20but%20that%20I%20must%20be%20here%20now%20with%20my%20family.%20Everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20felt%20all%20these%20years%20about%20living%20here%20is%C2%A0%20coming%20to%20the%20surface%20at%20once%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandparents%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ecannot%20leave%20because%20they%20are%20too%20old%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20is%20not%20going%20to%20leave%20them%20here.%20What%20if%20the%20situation%20gets%20so%20bad%20that%20my%20family%20tells%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20go%20to%20the%20United%20States%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20myself%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20crying.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20I%20do%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks%20herself.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20maternal%20side%20of%20her%20family%20has%20lived%20here%20for%20at%20least%20seven%20generations%2C%20much%20before%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20was%20created%20in%201948.%20Her%20paternal%20family%20are%20Holocaust%20survivors%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20immigrated%20to%20Israel%20after%201948.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20invited%20friends%20for%20dinner.%20All%20my%20Jewish%20friends%20who%20oppose%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20are%20distressed%20by%20what%20they%20are%20seeing%20on%20social%20media%20and%20what%20people%20around%20them%20are%20saying.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20surrounded%20by%20pro-Israeli%20discourse.%20These%20friends%20are%20horrified%20and%20repulsed%20by%20how%20their%20family%2C%20friends%20and%20acquaintances%20are%20legitimising%20the%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20and%20dehumanising%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20toll%20from%20Gaza%20just%20surpassed%20Israeli%20deaths.%20Can%20we%20stop%20now%2C%20or%20is%20that%20not%20enough%3F%E2%80%9D%20posted%20an%20Israeli-American%20on%20Instagram.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20expect%20that%20people%20will%20understand%20that%20levying%20collective%20punishment%20on%20Gaza%20in%20response%20to%20what%20Hamas%20did%20is%20immoral%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20Israeli%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20can%20they%20at%20least%20see%20that%20this%20strategy%20has%20not%20made%20us%20safe%20over%20the%20decades%3F%E2%80%9D%20An%20Israeli-American%20friend%2C%20who%20refrains%20from%20posting%20anything%20on%20social%20media%2C%20had%20enough%20when%20her%20friends%20started%20posting%20about%20how%20Gazans%20are%20ungrateful%20that%20Israel%20provides%20them%20with%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20f**ing%20mansion%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20never%20had%20to%20worry%20about%20access%20to%20safe%20and%20clean%20drinking%20water%20whenever%20you%20want%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20you%20should%20take%20a%20second%20to%20think%20about%20your%20cold%20and%20removed%20statements%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20friends%20are%20more%20embedded%20in%20leftist%20circles%20than%20they%20are%20within%20Jewish%20ones%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20are%20infuriated%20that%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20left%E2%80%9D%20is%20demanding%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20room%20for%20mourning%20the%20Israeli%20civilians%20killed%20by%20Hamas%20militants.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Israeli%20friend%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20fed%20up%20with%20all%20the%20sheltered%20social%20justice%20warriors%20who%20read%20Franz%20Fanon%20and%20Edward%20Said%20once%20in%20their%20life%20and%20think%20that%20they%20have%20this%20whole%20conflict%20figured%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CHamas%E2%80%99%20goal%20is%20to%20replace%20a%20Jewish%20supremacist%20state%20with%20an%20Islamic%20theocracy%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20liberatory%20about%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%2C%20referring%20to%20people%20who%20see%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20actions%20as%20justifiable%20resistance%20against%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20What%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-what-its-like-to-be-a-palestinian-in-israel-prof-dalal-iriqat%5C%22%3EWhat%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20angry%20at%20what%20I%20am%20seeing%20on%20social%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20someone%20says%20at%20the%20dinner%20table.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20friend%20screams%20%E2%80%9CI%20fear%20the%20discourse!%E2%80%9D%20hysterically%20to%20make%20us%20all%20laugh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20text%20message%20on%20a%20group%20chat%2C%20addressed%20to%20Israeli%20and%20international%20activists%20who%20go%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20support%20Palestinian%20communities%20which%20are%20under%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20the%20army.%20These%20activists%20spend%20anywhere%20between%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20many%20weeks%20in%20these%20communities%2C%20helping%20Palestinians%20push%20back%20against%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20army.%20They%20use%20cameras%20and%20phones%20to%20film%20settlers%20when%20they%20come%20into%20these%20communities%20and%20intimidate%20or%20attack%20Palestinians%2C%20argue%20with%20them%2C%20and%20call%20the%20Israeli%20police.%20They%20film%20when%20the%20Israeli%20soldiers%20harass%20or%20use%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%2C%20hoping%20that%20the%20soldiers%20would%20moderate%20their%20behaviour%20because%20they%20are%20on%20camera%2C%20and%20any%20illegal%20behavior%20or%20arbitrary%20action%20by%20soldiers%20will%20be%20documented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20very%20alarmed%20on%20reading%20the%20text%20message%2C%20which%20says%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20has%20rapidly%20intensified.%20On%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20after%20two%20separate%20incidents%20of%20unprecedented%20violence%20and%20risk%20towards%20solidarity%20activists%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Wadi%20A-Siq%20and%20At-Tuwani%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20experienced%20Israeli%20activists%20had%20a%20meeting%20about%20the%20current%20situation%20and%20what%20it%20means%20for%20all%20of%20us%20as%20solidarity%20activists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20message%20then%20describes%20how%20in%20Wadi%20A-Siq%2C%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%20ziptied%20activists%20and%20held%20them%20captive%20for%20many%20hours%2C%20and%20took%20their%20phones%20and%20cameras%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20Settlers%20beating%20activists%20is%20common%2C%20but%20holding%20activists%20captive%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20for%20multiple%20hours%20nobody%20knew%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20captive%20activists.%20A%20settler-militia%20attacked%20At-Tuwani%20and%20opened%20fire%3B%20some%20activists%20were%20present%20there%20too.%20One%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20activists%20was%20shot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20that%20at%20this%20moment%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20actively%20or%20widely%20be%20inviting%20activists%20due%20to%20the%20current%20dangers.%20The%20drive%20down%20can%20be%20dangerous%2C%20and%20in%20the%20field%2C%20settlers%20and%20military%20(which%2C%20especially%20now%2C%20are%20indistinguishable%20because%20settlers%20are%20wearing%20army%20uniforms)%20are%20very%20clearly%20ready%20with%20their%20fingers%20on%20the%20trigger.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinians%20from%20this%20region%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20which%20is%20called%20Masafar%20Yatta%20or%20South%20Hebron%20Hills%2C%20were%20describing%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20from%20the%20day%20the%20war%20began.%20But%20I%20am%20still%20shocked%20after%20reading%20the%20text%20messages%20because%20these%20activists%20making%20such%20a%20decision%20feels%20unprecedented.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20reaffirmation%20of%20how%20bad%20things%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faman-abhishek%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAman%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Abhishek%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20PhD%20student%20in%20media%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%2C%20USA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699250404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06110857%2Fsignal-2023-11-05-210917.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnotes-from-israel-palestine-gaza-holocaust%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20read%20of%20my%20friend%20Khalil%2C%20who%20has%20moved%20to%20south%20Gaza%20and%20is%20quoted%20in%20passing%20in%20news%20reports.%20It%20could%20be%20worse%20for%20him%3B%20he%20could%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20statistic%20%E2%80%93%20the%20number%20of%20displaced%2C%20wounded%2C%20and%20dead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnotes-from-israel-palestine-gaza-holocaust%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%3A%20In%20Dantewada%2C%20Maoist%20Threats%20Have%20Receded%20But%20Development%20Hasn't%20Come%20in%20Either%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105158%2FPipe-set-up-by-Bhuma-Tao-supplying-clean-water-e1699248803809.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDantewada%20(Chhattisgarh)%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIt%20is%20November%205.%20%3Cspan%3EThirty-two-year-old%20Bhuma%20Tamo%20is%20standing%20outside%20his%20tin-roof%20house%20in%20Dantewada%E2%80%99s%20Hiroli%20village.%20Tamo%20is%20watching%20men%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20cattle%20use%20the%20new%20water%20pipe%20that%20stands%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20away.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClean%20fresh%20water%20flows%20from%20the%20pipe.%20Villagers%20take%20baths%20and%20collect%20water.%20The%20cattle%20drink%20water%20from%20the%20vessels%20which%20have%20already%20