ndul%20complex%20of%20the%20NMDC%2C%20which%20operates%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Steel%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20southern%20tip%20of%20South%20Bastar%20in%20Dantewada%20district.%20It%20is%20surrounded%20by%20a%20range%20of%20hills%20that%20house%20deposits%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20rich%20in%20iron%20ore%20content%20and%20are%20rated%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20NDMC%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmdc.co.in%2Fabout-nmdc%2Foperating-mines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHiroli%20village%20lies%20just%20beyond%20the%20Kirandul%20complex.%20There%2C%20while%20residents%20worry%20about%20groundwater%20contamination%20from%20mining%2C%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20yet%20to%20see%20the%20fruits%20of%20development%2C%20including%20basic%20amenities%20such%20as%20metalled%20roads%2C%20pipe%20water%20connections%20and%20uninterrupted%20electricity%20supply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105244%2FNMDC-plant.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105244%2FNMDC-plant.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105244%2FNMDC-plant-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105244%2FNMDC-plant-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20NMDC%20plant.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20elections%20is%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20November%207%20and%2012%20of%20the%2020%20constituencies%20including%20Dantewada%2C%20are%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20tribal%20belt%20of%20the%20Bastar%20division.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong%20known%20as%20the%20bastion%20of%20Maoist%20activities%2C%20Dantewada%20has%20seen%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20incidents%20of%20Maoist%20violence%20over%20the%20years.%20This%20includes%20the%202010%20Naxal%20attack%20on%20a%20CRPF%20battalion%2C%20in%20which%2076%20jawans%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Tademetla%20forest%20area%20of%20Dantewada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%2010%20jawans%20of%20the%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20(DRG)%20and%20a%20civilian%20were%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchhattisgarh-11-killed-ied-blast-maoists-dantewada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20killed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20the%20vehicle%20they%20were%20travelling%20in%20was%20destroyed%20by%20an%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20(IED)%20triggered%20by%20Maoists%20in%20Dantewada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20worst%20such%20attack%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20since%20April%202021%2C%20when%2022%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20personnel%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20more%20injured%20during%20a%20gunfight%20with%20Maoists%20at%20the%20Sukma%20and%20Bijapur%20district%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%2015%20villages%20in%20Dantewada%20were%20declared%20%E2%80%9CMaoist-free%E2%80%9D%20on%20Independence%20Day.%20While%20locals%20say%20that%20Maoists%20are%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20much%20as%20earlier%2C%20development%20is%20something%20that%20evades%20them%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20all%20the%20facilities%20that%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20have%20that%20we%20feel%20we%20should%20also%20get%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tamo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20voted%20three%20times%20now%20and%20I%20will%20vote%20this%20time%20as%20well.%20Every%20time%20I%20go%20vote%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20things%20will%20change%20and%20we%20will%20also%20get%20development.%20But%20nothing%20has%20changed%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105214%2FRoad-in-Hiroli-village.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105214%2FRoad-in-Hiroli-village.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105214%2FRoad-in-Hiroli-village-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105214%2FRoad-in-Hiroli-village-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20road%20in%20Hiroli%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CAdivasis%20have%20nothing%20here%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census2011.co.in%2Fcensus%2Fdistrict%2F501-dantewada.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202011%252C%2520Dantewada%2520had%2520population%2Cwere%2520264%252C142%2520and%2520269%252C496%2520respectively.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2011%20Census%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EDantewada%20has%20a%20population%20of%205%2C33%2C638.%20The%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%202023%2C%20which%20uses%20NFHS%205%20data%20from%202019-2021%2C%20shows%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitallibrary.in.one.un.org%2FTempPdfFiles%2F8243_1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E29.53%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Dantewada%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20multidimensionally%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20district%20ranks%20sixth%20in%20the%20state%20on%20the%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%20after%20Bijapur%2C%20Sukma%2C%20Narayanpur%2C%20Bastar%2C%20Balarampur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20flags%20of%20both%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20a%20few%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%2C%20on%20the%20trees%20all%20around%20the%20mud%20roads%20leading%20to%20Hiroli.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYoung%20villagers%20say%20that%20politicians%20come%20to%20campaign%20before%20elections%2C%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20adivasis%20are%20where%20they%20were%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAdivasis%20have%20nothing%20here.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20roads.%20There%20is%20a%20school%20in%20our%20village%20but%20till%2010th%20standard.%20We%20want%20roads%2C%20we%20want%20connections%20under%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20%5Bthe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20scheme%20to%20provide%20water%20pipe%20connections%20to%20every%20rural%20household%5D%2C%20we%20should%20get%20jobs.%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20Adivasis%20are%20where%20they%20were%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chhannu%20Netam%2C%2025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%2C%20who%20has%20studied%20till%20Class%2010%20says%20that%20he%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NMDC%E2%80%99s%20job%20entrance%20exam%20but%20did%20not%20get%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20work%20as%20a%20farm%20labourer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105340%2FChhanu-Netam-on-his-bike-with-friends.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105340%2FChhanu-Netam-on-his-bike-with-friends.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105340%2FChhanu-Netam-on-his-bike-with-friends-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105340%2FChhanu-Netam-on-his-bike-with-friends-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChhanu%20Netam%20on%20his%20bike%20with%20friends.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20says%20that%20only%20three%20villagers%20work%20at%20the%20nearby%20NMDC.%20A%20fourth%20was%20killed%20by%20Maoists%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20a%20police%20informer%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20encouragement%20to%20send%20children%20to%20schools.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20opening%20a%20school%20when%20no%20one%20is%20encouraged%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Netam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20visit%20before%20elections%20but%20they%20also%20come%20and%20just%20give%20their%20speeches.%20There%20is%20no%20scope%20to%20talk%20to%20us.%20There%20is%20no%20Maoist%20threat%20here%20now%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20development%20either.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVillagers%20have%20decided%20to%20quiz%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20CPI%20leaders.%20It%20is%20only%20based%20on%20their%20answers%20that%20they%20will%20decide%20who%20to%20vote%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20already%20seen%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20done%20nothing%20for%20us.%20We%20want%20to%20ask%20them%20what%20they%20will%20do%20for%20us%20and%20then%20we%20will%20decide%20who%20to%20vote%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20Netam%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Hiroli%2C%20a%20group%20of%20villagers%20from%20nearby%20Palnar%20who%20work%20on%20farmland%20through%20the%20week%20and%20set%20up%20weekly%20markets%20on%20Fridays%20and%20Saturdays%20in%20these%20two%20villages%20say%20that%20livelihood%20is%20the%20chief%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESunil%20Yadav%2C%2027%2C%20who%20has%20come%20to%20sell%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emahua%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efruit%20that%20is%20used%20to%20make%20the%20local%20liquor%2C%20said%20that%20while%20Dantewada%20may%20be%20known%20for%20Maoist%20activities%2C%20unemployment%20is%20the%20worry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDantewada%20is%20not%20just%20about%20Naxalwaad.%20We%20need%20jobs%2C%20private%20schools.%20If%20other%20areas%20are%20getting%20quality%20education%20then%20we%20should%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yadav.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105300%2FVillagers-from-Palnar-set-up-their-weekly-Saturday-market-in-Hiroli-village.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105300%2FVillagers-from-Palnar-set-up-their-weekly-Saturday-market-in-Hiroli-village.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105300%2FVillagers-from-Palnar-set-up-their-weekly-Saturday-market-in-Hiroli-village-300x245.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105300%2FVillagers-from-Palnar-set-up-their-weekly-Saturday-market-in-Hiroli-village-1024x837.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22981%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVillagers%20from%20Palnar%20set%20up%20their%20weekly%20Saturday%20market%20in%20Hiroli%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDevelopment%20%E2%80%98not%20possible%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOutside%20the%20villages%2C%20in%20a%20market%20place%20near%20Geedam%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Dantewada%20candidate%20Chavindra%20Karma%20is%20going%20shop%20to%20shop%20meeting%20people%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20Karma%20is%20the%20son%20of%20late%20Congress%20leader%20Mahendra%20Karma%20who%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Fop-ed%2Fright-place-wrong-arrangement%2Farticle4823988.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20killed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ealong%20with%20the%20entire%20top%20state%20leadership%20in%20the%20Sukma%20Maoist%20attack%20in%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavindra%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Devti%20Karma%2C%20has%20been%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20Dantewada%20after%20winning%20the%20by-election%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20had%20originally%20won%20the%20seat%20(its%20lone%20victory%20in%20the%2012-seat%20tribal%20Bastar%20belt)%20in%20the%202018%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20new%20Dantewada%20MLA%20Bhima%20Mandavi%20was%20killed%20by%20Maoists%20in%20an%20IED%20blast%20in%20April%202019%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Dantewada%20by-poll%20win%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%20in%20all%2012%20seats%20in%20Bastar%20division%2C%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20repeat%20its%20performance%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EKarma%20says%20that%20development%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20to%20Dantewada%E2%80%99s%20villages%20as%20the%20Congress%20is%20still%20undoing%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Raman%20Singh%20government%20that%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%2015%20years%20from%202003%20to%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%20two%20issues%20are%20important.%20Giving%20employment%20to%20the%20unemployed%20and%20to%20help%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20roads%20and%20development%20in%20villages%20like%20Hiroli%2C%20Karma%20said%20that%20the%20interior%20villages%20have%20many%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Hiroli%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20yet%20to%20build%20roads%20but%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20best.%20There%20are%20many%20issues%20in%20these%20interior%20villages.%20We%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20health%20and%20education.%20But%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20our%20first%20priority%20is%20to%20give%20employment.%20Congress%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20give%20jobs%20to%20the%20unemployed%20since%202018%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20that.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20private%20schools%20at%20the%20time%20because%20we%20are%20giving%20English%20medium%20education%20in%20government%20schools.%20After%2015%20years%20we%20have%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20BJP%20so%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20do%20many%20things.%20We%20have%20done%20many%20things.%20Without%20connectivity%20(in%20interior%20villages)%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20bring%20development.%20So%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20ensure%20connectivity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Chetram%20Arami%2C%20who%20is%20taking%20on%20Karma%20in%20Dantewada%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20says%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20development%20in%20Dantewada%E2%80%99s%20villages%20is%20because%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20did%20not%20allow%20the%20penetration%20of%20Union%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20government%20has%20stopped%20all%20schemes%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20giving.%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20has%20been%20stopped%20by%20the%20government%2C%20that%20is%20why%20there%20is%20no%20proper%20water%20connection.%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20given%20us%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20to%20build%20houses%20for%20everyone%20but%20the%20state%20government%20has%20stopped%20this%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArami%20said%20that%20once%20the%20BJP%20wins%20in%20Dantewada%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%20government%20will%20bring%20development%20not%20just%20in%20Dantewada%20but%20in%20the%20entire%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105232%2FPipe-set-up-by-Bhuma-Tao-supplying-water-to-people-and-cattle-in-the-village.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105232%2FPipe-set-up-by-Bhuma-Tao-supplying-water-to-people-and-cattle-in-the-village.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105232%2FPipe-set-up-by-Bhuma-Tao-supplying-water-to-people-and-cattle-in-the-village-300x262.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06105232%2FPipe-set-up-by-Bhuma-Tao-supplying-water-to-people-and-cattle-in-the-village-